{"ts":"2026-06-27T12:57:31.552Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Testing Support APIs**\n\nOkay, I'm focusing on the support ticket APIs. My current plan involves crafting `scripts/test-support-apis.js`. This script will thoroughly vet endpoints, specifically: `app/api/v1/support/route.ts` which includes the GET (list with query params) and POST (create) methods. I'm keen to ensure they are robust.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
